    <stitle>HOOD, GRILLE, FENDERS AND BUMPER - 7000 - 7000 Model Series - FENDER EXTENSIONS</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="1">
        <title>FENDER EXTENSIONS</title>
        <para>Fender Extensions are an integral part of the fender system on the 7000 series vehicles. The fender
            extensions have been designed to provide splash and spray protection (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f0900710">Figure 10, Item 1</hotlnk>). This protects the lower front of the cab from splash
            and road debris kicked up by the front tires, and it also keeps the step cleaner.
        </para>
        <figure id="f0900710" figsize="col-wide">
